description: Enhance your productivity with the Dell Multimedia Corbed Keyboard. This sleek, black membrane keyboard features chiclet-style keys for comfortable and responsive typing. The USB 2.0 connection provides a quick and reliable link to your computer. Weighing just 420g, the compact 127mm x 442mm x 24mm dimensions mean this keyboard is ideal for any workspace. The one-year Dell warranty provides peace of mind. With its full QWERTY layout and membrane key switches, this keyboard makes typing easier than ever. The manufacturer's part number for this product is 580-AHHG. So get more done with the Dell Multimedia Corded Keyboard today!
